The wait is finally over … Season 5 of Workin’ Moms returns to Netflix! Get ready for a whole new season of the hilarious, and all too relatable, realities of juggling a career and a love life all while trying to raise kids.   If you’re looking for a refreshing break from your own action-packed life, you’ve found it. Betty Season 2 premieres today on Showmax. In season two, our five protagonists are stepping firmly into womanhood and tackling all the challenges it brings. As they navigate the pressures of adulthood, their male counterparts start to step up, step in, and become true allies, forming a united front for the greater good.   MI5 security officer Eve Polastri is bored in her job and yearns for a more exciting life. When a Russian politician is murdered, Eve is tasked with protecting the only witness and soon finds herself on a collision course with the violent and extraordinary assassin, Villanelle. Do not miss Killing Eve, Season 1 Thursdays on SABC 3 at 9pm.  